title: MisterMusic Show 324 - indie,alternative,rock Radio
description:
MisterMusic Show 324 - 192 kbps MP3 -120 mins.



I have new music on the show this week from Weezer, Apes, Johnny Marr, Erlend Oye, and another new song off the latest U2 album.

Plus the''Oldie of the Week'' - a number 1 hit on the US modern rock chart 22 years ago in October 1992.
It's over 5 decades of indie, alternative and classic rock hits.

Thanks for tuning in.



The MisterMusic Show is broadcast weekly and heard globally on RockXS internet radio.
